id: pm-github-1nlw
title: Spawn pm.cmd via shell on win32 in export test workspace helper
description: "Follow-up to #31: execFileSync of the pm.cmd shim on Windows fails with EINVAL under the CVE-2024-27980 mitigation unless run through a shell. Add shell:process.platform==='win32' to makeExportTestWorkspace spawns (args are static test values, so shell:true is safe). Test-only; mirrors the pm-jira #26 fix flagged by CodeRabbit."
