author: claude-opus
resolution: "Added shell:win32 to makeExportTestWorkspace execFileSync spawns"
expected_result: pm.cmd runs via shell on Windows without EINVAL
actual_result: Setup spawns shell out on win32; 99/99 tests pass on Linux CI
